snippet.textDisplay: This was produced really well, I felt like Abida Parveen was kind of guiding Naseebo Lal to accept life as it is. And it felt like she was accepting her and encouraging her to love herself and submit to God. I felt it thru the song and I could sense that Naseebo lal believed in herself after the song was done. I could feel the love between them. And I could sense that they both knew that they are the same, they are one. Peace and love.
